The paper proposes a new signature scheme for efficient authentication in IoT applications with stringent minimum-delay requirements. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Information Theory (cs.IT), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), Systems and Control (cs.SY), and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
